{"id":442218,"date":[{"year":1963,"month":4,"day":10}],"page":"4","source":"","region":"","masthead":"","special_issue":"笔会","column":"南京路上好八连战士诗选","genre":"","count":"149","ytitle":"","mtitle":"指导员的家当","ftitle":"","authors":["孙一广"],"text":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"一只装肥皂的木箱，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"指导员用它装家当:"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一双老布鞋，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"两件旧军装。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一只装肥皂的木箱，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"指导员用它装家当:"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"革命战士的俭朴生活习惯，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"无产者的崇高理想。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"指导员真正的家当，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"在九百六十万平方公里的土地上，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"在走向社会主义的道路上，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"在六亿五千万人民的心上……"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"(以上三首为孙一广作)"}]}